<h1>Fanfare is basically a section dedicated to the fans of <i>Ecco the Dolphin</i>. Each section is divided by fan and consists of a profile, artwork, stories and music. 

<p>To look for artwork, for example, simply click on a user's name and you will be taken to a section that's almost a mini-site, which contains everything you want to know about that user.</p>

All artwork, stories and music must be related to <i>Ecco the Dolphin</i>, dolphins, or the underwater theme.

<p>If you would like to make a profile for yourself please click <a href='update-profile.pl'>"Create Profile"</a>.
<br />
If you would like to send fan artwork, fan fiction, fan music please email them to <a href='mailto:arkonviox@arkonviox.net'>
Arkonviox@arkonviox.net</a>.</p>

<p align='center'>Please make sure to check out our <a href='display.pl?id=art-contest'>Art Contest</a> for a chance to win two hundred dollars!</p>
</h1>

